snippet.title: Are Bots Signing Anti Amber Heard Petitions? | Flixet
snippet.description:
In this video, we are going to share are bots signing anti amber heard petitions? 

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
___________________________________________________

An online petition calling on Warner Bros. to remove Amber Heard from the next mast in the "Aquaman 2" comic has collected more than 1.6 million signatures and is rapidly approaching the 2 million mark.


Music In This Video : 

Track: Odessa — LiQWYD & Scandinavianz
Music provided by Audio Library Plus
Watch: https://youtu.be/jNy-Dp3lgcg
